---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Experience - Bradley Spillert">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="section-heading fade-in">Experience</h1>

      <div class="space-y-16">
        <!-- Lumafield -->
        <div class="fade-in">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-medium">
                <a href="https://www.lumafield.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lumafield</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Sr Software Engineer &middot; Cambridge, MA</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">2021 -- 2026</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>
              Joined as the first mechatronics hire and grew into the tech lead for embedded software. Worked on both scanner platforms -- Neptune and Triton -- from breadboard prototypes to shipping production units. The job was everything from writing device drivers for scientific X-ray cameras to standing up a manufacturing line.
            </p>
            <p>
              Shipped hundreds of production scanners. Wrote firmware in C for custom STM32 control boards, built image acquisition pipelines in Python and OpenCV, and designed the networking layer between embedded Linux hosts and microcontroller subsystems.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
              Python, C/C++, Linux, OpenCV, STM32, I2C/SPI/UART, PCB bring-up
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Enel FT -->
        <div class="fade-in">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-medium">
                <a href="https://www.enelgreenpower.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Enel Green Power</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">I&C Engineer &middot; Andover, MA</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">2021</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>
              Instrumentation and controls on the Ranchland project -- a 1 GW wind and battery storage facility in Oklahoma. SCADA configuration, control system integration, and commissioning support for one of the largest wind-storage hybrids in North America.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
              SCADA, MATLAB, wind energy, battery storage, controls
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Enel Intern -->
        <div class="fade-in">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-medium">
                <a href="https://www.enelgreenpower.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Enel Green Power</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">EE Intern &middot; Andover, MA</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">2019</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>
              Summer internship on the Roadrunner solar and battery storage project in New Mexico. First real exposure to industrial controls -- the kind of systems where a misconfigured relay trips an entire substation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Education -->
        <div class="fade-in pt-8 border-t border-white/[0.04]">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-medium">
                <a href="https://www.umass.edu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UMass Amherst</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">BS Computer Engineering</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">2021</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <p>
              Capstone: Gyro Glove -- a wearable gesture controller for RC aircraft. Tilt your hand, fly the plane. Won Best Hardware Hack at HackUMass with a polar plotter built in 36 hours.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
